    dc:description "FIGURES 87 – 92, Stephanollona arborescens n. sp., MZUSP 349 (part of the paratype specimen), off São Paulo, Brazil. 87, Colony with some large avicularia; 88, colony with some ovicelled zooids; 89, close-up of large avicularia; 90, some ovicelled zooid; 91, close-up of ovicelled zooid with large rounded pore; 92, close-up of orifice with six oral spines." ;
